T|Novi|0|ROAS: No signal. IG baselines are "[not yet recorded]" across all metrics. The an pipeline — Instagram scraper → sb social_snapshots — was architected but never primed. No historical perf data exists to set a ROAS target or assess current cg efficiency. The SS26 cg (late June launch) will go live w/o a single pre-cg perf baseline.
T|Novi|1|Budget: Cannot recommend — no data. Budget recommendations require at minimum: (a) current ad spend, (b) last 30-day ROAS by cg/ad set, (c) CPM and CTR tn on Meta. None of these exist. Do not allocate budget blindly. Base rate risk: DTC fashion brands launching w/o established engagement baselines underperform by 30-40% on first-month ROAS (per ka).
T|Novi|2|Creative: No running ad sets to flag as stale (>21 days). SS26 creative is in dv w/ ln (cp) + at (visual direction) + px (production). cg not yet launched. Recommendation: When creative goes live, set calendar reminder for 21-day freshness check per ad set.
T|Novi|3|Platform Mix: Meta + Instagram ad only (per vt lock in ag.md — no TikTok before Q3 2026 rv). No current spend to assess mix efficiency.
T|Novi|4|kh gate: Not required — no budget change being recommended (no data to base a change on).
T|Novi|5|
T|What|0|Prime the pipeline: Trigger POST /ap/instagram for nz → populate social_snapshots w/ current baseline (followers, engagement rate, Reels reach, static post perf). This is a single ap call.
T|What|1|Historical benchmark: Once snapshot lands, run Reels vs. static cn perf al — this directly feeds the cn mix decision pnd since April 15.
T|What|2|Meta ad Manager export: If any cg ran historically (even tst cg), export last 90 days of perf data: spend, impressions, CTR, CPM, conversions, ROAS by ad set.
T|What|3|Commit to a baseline cadence: Weekly IG snapshots so ro has a rolling dataset by the time SS26 goes live.
T|What|4|
T|Pre-|0|Per ro's operating rules (ag.md): a pre-mortem is required before every cg launch. SS26 is targeting late June — w/ no perf baseline, the pre-mortem shd explicitly address the "blind launch" scenario: what happens if ROAS is sub-1.5x in the first 14 days w/ no historical data to guide reallocation. This shd be run jointly w/ kh before any budget is committed.
