T|Hour|0|CAC: No signal. hb is pre-launch — no pd, no us, no pricing md, no acquisition channels. The metrics table is entirely "[fill in]" or "[not yet recorded]" across all 12 KPIs. ka's analytical fn for hb (LinkedIn metrics, cohort retention, churn signals) is structurally defined but cannot activate bc the conditions for measurement do not exist.
T|Hour|1|Budget: Maintain at $0. No pd to advertise. LinkedIn ad spend shd not begin until: (1) fx completes runway al + pricing recommendation (HRB-002), (2) pricing is approved, (3) dv builds trial-to-paid funnel (HRB-001), (4) first cohort enters the funnel. Only at step 4 does paid acquisition have something to op toward.
T|Hour|2|Targeting: Premature to specify. LinkedIn targeting (working professionals, excluding HNWIs and wealth management — per ag.md targeting spec) cannot be refined w/o: (a) ICP validation from first organic signups, (b) trial-to-paid conversion data showing which segments convert, (c) fx's LTV md to define allowable CAC.
T|Hour|3|LTV:CAC wn: N/A — neither LTV nor CAC can be calculated. Pricing md pnd (HRB-002), pd not built (HRB-001). The 2:1 LTV:CAC alert threshold (escalate to mc immediately) is pre-configured in ag.md but cannot fire w/o data.
T|Hour|4|kh gate: Not required — no spend, no change.
