T|Stru|0|ka's recommendation to define the an sc now — before the pd is built — is correct and ro endorses it. Specifically: if hb ships w/o event instrumentation (signup, trial start, first workspace, first transaction, invite sent, upgrade), ro will have no conversion data to op LinkedIn cg against for the first 90 days post-launch. This is a known fl mode in B2B SaaS — retroactive instrumentation costs 3-5x more engineering time than baking it in from day one.
